import torchvision.transforms as transforms
import torchvision.transforms.functional as F
from PIL import Image
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


rotate_transform = transforms.RandomRotation(degrees=360)
translate_transform = transforms.RandomAffine(degrees=0, translate=(0.1, 0.1))
scale_transform = transforms.RandomAffine(degrees=0, scale=(0.8, 1.2))
perspective_transform = transforms.RandomPerspective(distortion_scale=0.2, p=0.2, interpolation=F.InterpolationMode.BILINEAR)

# 组合所有增强变换
transform = transforms.Compose([
    rotate_transform,
    translate_transform,
    scale_transform,
    perspective_transform,
    transforms.ToTensor()
])

# 加载图像
image_path = 'stamp216751.jpg'
image = Image.open(image_path).resize((512, 512))

# 应用变换并可视化结果
fig, axes = plt.subplots(5, 5, figsize=(20, 20))
for i in range(25):
    transformed_image = transform(image)
    transformed_image = transforms.ToPILImage()(transformed_image)
    row = i // 5
    col = i % 5   
    axes[row, col].imshow(transformed_image)
    axes[row, col].axis('off')
plt.show()
